e=3D"disabled" isauthor=3D""><h4>2.10 Earning through Partners</h4>
<p>Points earned in connection with the partner are subject to these Loyalt=
y Program Rules along with any applicable terms and conditions of the partn=
er.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;">2.10.a. <i>Miles to Points Offering</i>. =
A Member may convert Miles to Points with select frequent flyer programs or=
 other affiliated airline programs (each, a =E2=80=9CParticipating Airline=
=E2=80=9D) at a designated Miles to Points conversion ratio as indicated <u=
><a href=3D"https://www.marriott.com/loyalty/earn/miles/miles-to-points.mi"=
>here</a></u> (the =E2=80=9CMiles to Points Offering=E2=80=9D). Registratio=
n for the Miles to Points Offering is not required but may be subject to el=
igibility criteria, from time to time, as set forth by Participating Airlin=
es and the Marriott Bonvoy Loyalty Program. Members requesting to convert M=
iles earned through Participating Airlines to Points with the Marriott Bonv=
oy Loyalty Program must be a member of both the Marriott Bonvoy Loyalty Pro=
gram and the Participating Airline in order to successfully complete the co=
nversion. Members engaging in the Miles to Points Offering are required to =
ensure that the account holder name in both their Participating Airline acc=
ount and Marriott Bonvoy Loyalty Program Account match to ensure that the M=
iles to Points Offering transaction successfully posts to the Account. Once=
 Miles have been converted to Points, Points will automatically be transfer=
red to the Member=E2=80=99s Marriott Bonvoy Loyalty Program Account. In mos=
t cases, Points will be posted to the Member=E2=80=99s Marriott Bonvoy Loya=
lty Program Account in up to eight (8) weeks. Once Points are ordered to a =
Member=E2=80=99s Marriott Bonvoy Loyalty Program Account, cancellation, cha=
nges, reissuance, and/or refunds of Miles are not allowed. The Marriott Bon=
voy Loyalty Program and Participating Airlines have the right to terminate =
the Miles to Points Offering or to change the Miles to Points Offering poli=
cies, procedures, conditions of participation, benefits, awards and special=
 offers, in whole or in part, at any time, with or without notice. The Marr=
iott Bonvoy Loyalty Program reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to =
prevent or cancel transactions where (i) the Loyalty Program has reason to =
believe that the identity of the Member converting the Miles to Points does=
 not match the identity of the person receiving the Points or (ii) where th=
e Loyalty Program suspects there has been any fraudulent activity connected=
 with the Miles to Points conversion in relation to the Member=E2=80=99s Ac=
count. For details on joining Participating Airline, please refer to the pa=
rticular Participating Airline=E2=80=99s terms and conditions. The terms an=
d conditions of each Participating Airline control the distribution of the =
Miles earned through Participating Airline. The Miles to Points Offering is=
 subject to the terms and conditions of each Participating Airline.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;">2.10.b. <i>Cruise with Points.</i> A Memb=
er may earn Points when he/she books a cruise through the Company=E2=80=99s=
 cruise partner. More information on the Cruise with Points program may be =
obtained <a target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Link to Cruise with Points" href=3D"=
https://cruise-with-points.marriott.com/" aria-label=3D"here Clickable link=
 Opens in new tab / window"><u>here</u></a>=E2=86=97. This section does not=
 apply to The Ritz-Carlton Yacht Collection (see 1.2.a for The Ritz-Carlton=
 Yacht Collection).</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;">2.10.c. <i>Hertz=C2=AE, Dollar=C2=AE, Thr=
ifty=C2=AE.</i> A member may earn Points and receive special discounts on v=
ehicle rentals with Hertz, Dollar, and Thrifty, where available, when booke=
d through <a target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Link to Activities" href=3D"https:/=
/urldefense.com/v3/__https:/activities.marriott.com/cars__;!!Hj__v3g!cnLf6g=
6Mh1X_bepD6qklSq2bc3XmBpzLfFRw5fXs0Vs1fLymSokJ-N7rQ75-hnXwj9s_Qn7Aiyn_cGu7Q=
o-nBSra6d92WQ$" aria-label=3D"here Clickable link Opens in new tab / window=
"><u>here</u></a>=E2=86=97. Qualified Elite Members may also receive compli=
mentary Hertz Gold Plus Rewards=C2=AE elite status.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;">2.10.d. <i>Vacations by Marriott Bonvoy.<=
/i> Vacations by Marriott Bonvoy is administered by a third-party travel pa=
rtner on behalf of the Loyalty Program On-property Member Benefits, Points =
and Elite Night Credit are earned in accordance with the Loyalty Program Ru=
les. Members cannot use Points or Miles to purchase Vacations by Marriott B=
onvoy packages. Members are subject to the Loyalty Program Rules as well as=
