<p style=3D"margin-left: 120.0px;">A. <i>Nightly Upgrade Awards. </i>Nightl=
y Upgrade Awards may be redeemed for advance confirmable upgrades for selec=
t Premium Rooms or suites on a per room, per night basis, subject to availa=
bility and the applicable terms and conditions set forth below for Nightly =
Upgrade Awards:</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(1) Nightly Upgrade Awards expire on 31 =
December of the year following the year in which they were earned and must =
be used before they expire as they cannot be extended. For example, if 50 o=
r 75 Qualifying Nights are achieved in 2026 and five (5) Nightly Upgrade Aw=
ards are selected as the Member=E2=80=99s Annual Choice Benefit, the five (=
5) Nightly Upgrade Awards must be used on Loyalty Program eligible paid sta=
ys and/or Award Redemption Stays on or before 31 December 2027.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(2) Nightly Upgrade Awards may be used o=
nly on Loyalty Program eligible paid stays as well as Award Redemption Stay=
s.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(3) A Member may request to use their Ni=
ghtly Upgrade Awards on Marriott Websites or by calling <a href=3D"https://=
www.marriott.com/help/loyalty-customer-support.mi"><u><b>Member Support</b>=
</u></a>.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(4) Nightly Upgrade Awards may only be u=
sed for Premium Rooms and suites as designated by the Participating Propert=
y. Some suite types may not be available for use with Nightly Upgrade Award=
s.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(5) Nightly Upgrade Award use is based u=
pon availability of the requested suite or Premium Room. Checking for avail=
ability begins as early as five (5) days before arrival (for all brands exc=
ept for EDITION, the Ritz-Carlton, and the St. Regis where fulfilment will =
begin at three (3) days prior to arrival). Availability is checked each day=
 before arrival up until around 2 p.m. local time of the Participating Prop=
erty one (1) day prior to arrival. If at that time Nightly Upgrade Awards c=
annot be confirmed, the Nightly Upgrade Awards are credited back to the Mem=
ber's account if they have not expired.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(6) Nightly Upgrade Awards may be used o=
nly when there are enough in the Member's Account so that one (1) is applie=
d to every night of the reservation. One Nightly Upgrade Award is required =
per room per night.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(7) Nightly Upgrade Awards are required =
for each night of the stay including any nights that may be designated =E2=
=80=9Cfree=E2=80=9D. This includes the Stay for 5, Pay for 4 Offer describe=
d in Section 3.3.d. where a Nightly Upgrade Award is required for every nig=
ht of the stay, even the free night(s).</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(8) Nightly Upgrade Awards may not be tr=
ansferred or given as a gift or used as part of a multiple room reservation=
; however, a Member may use Nightly Upgrade Awards for additional single-ro=
om reservations during a stay as long as the Member is present for the stay=
 and the other reservations are under the Member's name.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(9) Members who book separate reservatio=
ns for consecutive nights that precede or follow a reservation that has con=
firmed Nightly Upgrade Awards will be required to change rooms to the confi=
rmed room type on any night(s) where a Nightly Upgrade Award is not used.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(10) If a Participating Property offers =
multiple room options for a Nightly Upgrade Award, once the suite or premiu=
m room option(s) is selected, the selection may be changed until 2 p.m. loc=
al time of the Participating Property one (1) day prior to arrival so long =
as the Nightly Upgrade Award is unconfirmed. A member can only change their=
 requested room pool(s) prior to approval or denial of the Nightly Upgrade =
Award.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(11) Nightly Upgrade Awards have request=
ing, booking, cancellation, and modification policies that are in addition =
to =E2=80=93 but completely separate from =E2=80=93 the booking, cancellati=
on, and modification policies for the reservations on which they are used.<=
/p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(a) Requests to use Nightly Upgrade Awar=
ds on a reservation may be made up to 2 p.m. local time of the Participatin=
g Property one (1) day prior to arrival.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(b) Requests to withdraw the use of unco=
nfirmed Nightly Upgrade Awards may be made up to 2 p.m. local time of the P=
articipating Property one (1) day prior to arrival.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(c) Confirmed Nightly Upgrade Awards may=
 be cancelled up to 2 p.m. local time of the Participating Property one (1)=
 day prior to arrival only if the entire reservation is cancelled.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(d) Once Nightly Upgrade Awards have bee=
n confirmed, the Member must cancel the entire reservation to receive credi=
t back for all Nightly Upgrade Awards. Cancellation of a confirmed Nightly =
Upgrade Award reservation after 2 p.m. local time of the Participating Prop=
erty one (1) day prior to arrival will result in the forfeiture of all Nigh=
tly Upgrade Awards applied to the entire reservation.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(e) Nightly Upgrade Awards cannot be app=
lied to a reservation once the reservation has been checked-in to a Partici=
pating Property.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(f) If a Member departs a reservation ea=
rly, any unused Nightly Upgrade Awards confirmed for the stay will be forfe=
ited.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 180.0px;">(g) If a Member wishes to extend their s=
tay and has enough Nightly Upgrade Award(s) to cover the extension, the Mem=
ber must book a separate reservation for the additional nights and request =
to use Nightly Upgrade Awards on Marriott Websites or by calling Member Sup=
port; the Nightly Upgrade Award request cannot be processed at the Particip=
ating Property. Nightly Upgrade Award use is based on availability of the r=
equested suite or premium room. Checking for availability begins as early a=
s five (5) days before arrival (for all brands except for EDITION, The Ritz=
-Carlton, and the St. Regis where fulfilment will begin at three (3) days p=
rior to arrival), and up until around 2 p.m. local time of the Participatin=
g Property one (1) day prior to the start of the separate reservation. Memb=
ers who book separate reservations for consecutive nights that precede or f=
ollow a reservation that has confirmed Nightly Upgrade Awards may be requir=
ed to change rooms.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(12) Not all Participating Properties pa=
rticipate in Nightly Upgrade Awards. Nightly Upgrade Awards are not redeema=
ble at the following brands: All-Inclusive Resorts, Marriott Executive Apar=
tments, Marriott Grand Residence Club, Marriott Vacation Club, Ritz-Carlton=
 Reserve, Sheraton Vacation Club, StudioRes, The Phoenician Residences, a L=
