 Nightly Upgrade Awards are not redeemable at properties that do not partic=
ipate in Marriott Bonvoy.</p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 140.0px;">(13) Nightly Upgrade Awards will be plac=
ed in the Member Account within 48 hours of when a Member selects an Annual=
 Choice Benefit of five (5) Nightly Upgrade Awards.</p>
