e=3D"disabled" isauthor=3D""><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;">4.3.e. <b>Ma=
rriott Bonvoy Ambassador Elite Membership Benefits</b>. In addition to all =
of the benefits Titanium Elite Members receive, Elite Members who reach 100=
 Qualifying Nights or more and at least $23,000 U.S. dollars in Annual Qual=
ifying Spend based on Qualifying Charges earned on completed Stays in a Qua=
lifying Period (does not include Qualifying Charges made in advance for Sta=
ys in the year(s) following the Qualifying Period such as for pre-paid stay=
